  "title": "Junior Accountant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable.</p></li><li><p>Handle invoicing, payments, and staff claims.</p></li><li><p>Follow up with clients for outstanding payments.</p></li><li><p>Prepare financial reports and statements.</p></li><li><p>Perform bank reconciliations and monitor cash flow.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper filing and documentation of financial records.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Accounting or related field.</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of accounting principles and practices.</p></li><li><p>Experience with accounting software (e.g., Xero).</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Excel and data entry.</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented, organized, and able to meet deadlines.</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills to follow up with clients professionally.</p></li></ul>",
